---
title: Creamy Mushroom Ravioli with Herby Garlic Sauce
description: Stuffed ravioli and slow roasted mushrooms and cauliflower combine in an herby garlic cream sauce. The flavours will dance on your tongue while you gobble up every last bit of this hearty ravioli dinner.
